<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ج - التَّعْرِيْفُ بِرِجَالِهِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>د - شُرُوْحُهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>هـ - أَطْرَافُهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>و- تَخْرِيْجُ أَحَادِيْثِهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>ز - طِبَاعَتُهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>ح - مَنْهَجُهُ فِيْهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>ط - انْتِقَاؤُهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>ي - زَوَائِدُهُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>ك - المُسْتَخْرَجُ عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">الفَصْلُ السَّادِسُ:</span> ثَنَاءُ العُلَمَاء عَلَيْهِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">الفَصْلُ السَّابِعُ:</span> إِمَامَتُهُ فِي الجَرْحِ وَالتَّعْدِيْل، وَالتَّصْحِيْحِ وَالتَّعْلِيْل<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">وَقَدْ خَتَمْتُ عَمَلِي فِي كِتَابِي هَذَا بِأَرْبَعَةِ فَهَارِس:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">فِهْرِس:</span> للرُّوَاة المُتَرْجَمِ لَهُم فِيْهِ:<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">فِهْرِس:</span> للنِّسَبِ المُعَرَّف بِهَا فِيْهِ:<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">فِهْرِس:</span> لِمَصَادِرِ البَحْثِ الَّتِي نَقَلْتُ مِنْهَا،<span class="c5"> وَهِي عَلَى قِسْمَيْن:</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>- المَصَادِرُ المَطْبُوْعَة.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>- والمَصَادِرُ المَخْطُوْطَة، أَوْ مَا هُوَ فِي حُكْمِهَا، كَالرَّسَائِل الجَامِعِيّةِ الَّتِي لَمْ تُطْبَعْ بَعْدُ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c5">فِهْرِس:</span> المَوْضُوْعَات.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>